title.rendered: ACI Presents Distinguished Achievement Award to Alticor Inc

content.rendered:
The American Concrete Institute (ACI) presented its Distinguished Achievement Award to Alticor Inc. The award was presented at the ACI Fall 2013 Convention in Phoenix, Arizona, October 20.

The award is typically given to ACI nonmembers who have made notable contributions to the advancement of the concrete industry. Alticor Inc were honored for providing leadership in the advancement of the sustainable use of concrete through innovation and efficient use of local resources.

Click here for Press Release
